<p>I‚Äôm a member of the Network Infrastructure business group in this company. Most of my customers are network engineers who are supporting the design, testing, and migration operations of ISPs and/or GSM operators. We can group all these operations under two categories: <strong>greenfield deployments</strong> and <strong>migrations</strong>.</p>

